{"tid":2382840,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"港爸怨跟足指引領養被拒遭滋擾報警 貓義工稱家居不安全","createTime":"2021-01-27T13:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T11:06:08.000Z","uid":82845,"like":34,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f565443383032a8af14667ecfe58aafb7a81db2c","tid":2382840,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/148108245239100/posts/3637993932917163/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F148108245239100%2Fposts%2F3637993932917163%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=5ed019a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/148108245239100/posts/3637993932917163/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n協助動物尋家的義工行為操守向來有爭議，有單親爸爸抱怨依照義工的指引以及完成家訪，義工因為籠太細，拒絕將一隻貓「芝麻」送交領養，還索取200多元的士費以及人身滋擾跟蹤，網民其後到警署報案。不過義工方面就質疑男事主的家及生活方式，根本不適合照顧貓隻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1983876/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Juicy%E5%8F%AE-%E6%B8%AF%E7%88%B8%E6%80%A8%E9%81%B5%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%8A%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E9%81%AD%E6%BB%8B%E6%93%BE%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6-%E8%B2%93%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%B1%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1983876%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Juicy%25E5%258F%25AE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2588%25B8%25E6%2580%25A8%25E9%2581%25B5%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25BB%258B%25E6%2593%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25B2%2593%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=4a39a63f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1983876%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%2