T13:01:36.000Z","msg":"3個月前嘅我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手養貓賭大細，完全唔識人，不過我比較保險，喺一間大機構領養。我個貓義工小姐好好人，嚟家訪都好聲好氣，接咗隻貓返嚟都keep住聯絡，我問佢好多嘢佢都逐一答我，仲教咗我好多貓奴知識。前幾日仲介紹獸醫俾我絕育。我起初都以為貓義工會好閪，結果同連登講嘅完全兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我個貓義工實在太好人，所以我要幫佢(=貓義工)平反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e114e29e5fbfb4f742bef4b53666765d4d745aa","tid":2382840,"uid":374389,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"29da2b042850d0fedc2f0c72c035178019a867b8","tid":2382840,"uid":299372,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c70e47478ba1b97e98e826cc170e652a37de8ab2","tid":2382840,"uid":374389,"like":6,"dislike":20,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"b80a87caf4225f4950b7a5419f48626be440eef8","tid":2382840,"uid":299372,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"好多繁殖撚上黎搵食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"同埋好多黑店老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上嚟係咁唱衰啲貓義工等自己呃到飯碗搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔未領養過就信晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為全香港嘅貓義工都仆街<br />\n試都唔試吓領養就去買貓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"係，雖然部分貓義工抵屌，但唔少都好熱心幫貓幫人<br />\n好多巴絲都有放d好義工contact出黎話自己成功領養，但又冇人會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家圍爐屌柒貓義工再推廣買寵物就算<br />\n仲有d根本無養寵物既出黎煽風點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(係其他post見到條友話自己唔會養寵物,但個個唱衰貓義工post都見到佢<i